data.description: Opportunity knocks! This property is a canvas for the visionary. Calling all astute investors and savvy homebuyer- this is your chance to step into a realm of potential. With motivated sellers, this home is at an unbeatable price!! This space holds the promise of becoming a masterpiece for investors seeking value or for those eager to craft their dream home through gradual renovations. Picture to the right, a generously sized living room, easily adaptable to suite your needs- be it serene sitting room or a functional office. Discover a formal dining area seamlessly connected to an open kitchen, boasting ample cabinet and counter space. Imaging the joy of entertaining in your kitchen with an abundance of natural light, offering picturesque views of the back yard. But the real charm lies in the home's character-the family room adorned with bookshelves surrounding a gas fireplace, creating the ideal ambiance for relaxation. In addition, the convenience of accessing the large concrete patio from the kitchen creates an indoor-outdoor flow for entertainment. Head out the sliding glass door to your side entry 2 car garage with ample driveway parking and basketball court for the kids. , the Owner's suite boasts a generous size, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and bathroom. Community has optional/voluntary HOA. Current owners are not contributing but future owner can. Home Sold AS IS. Don't miss out on this golden opportunity-the perfect blend of potential and promise awaits! Property is sold as-is and priced below market for quick sale. Seller is willing to offer $10,000 flex allowance to be used for buyer's choice of closing costs, and/or interest rate buy down with full price offer. Key Features: New architectural roof already done in October 2023, New water heater, and contemporary finishes. Easy showing via Showingtime. Property qualifies for 100% financing with no PMI using the Path Loan Program.
